int jt_replace_nids ( int  argc,
char **  argv 
)

Replace nids for given device.

lctl replace_nids <devicename> <nid1>[,nid2,nid3] Command should be started on MGS server. Only MGS server should be started (command execution returns error in another cases). Command mount -t lustre <MDT partition>=""> -o nosvc <mount point>=""> can be used for that.

llogs for MDTs and clients are processed. All records copied as is except add_uuid and setup. This records are skipped and recorded with new nids and uuid.

See also:
